title: Ryde or Die
subTitle: An Uber driver experiences a night of terror after a fare forces him to participate in a series of violent road games.

title: Lyco
subTitle: Lyco Fontaine, a voodoo priest, searches for an ancient relic that has been around for centuries.

title: The 27 Club
subTitle: A singer-songwriter chasing fame and a journalism student researching his thesis are drawn into a sinister underworld as they attempt to discover the truth behind the curse of "The 27 Club."

title: Rosa Leigh
subTitle: Four paranormal investigators seek to debunk the claims surrounding an abandoned school where a little girl, her teacher and the school's janitor were killed 60 years earlier.

title: Diane
subTitle: Steve's lingering physical and emotional scars from the war in Afghanistan plunge him into a soulless routine. He continues his drab existence until the corpse of a beautiful singer, Diane, is dumped in his backyard, shaking him back to reality. Steve takes a photo of her before calling the police, and he becomes obsessed with the dead woman's image. Steve is scrutinized by the police, becoming the prime suspect hassled by Diane's widower, and attacked by self-righteous neighbors.

title: Halloween P... Trap Kill! Kill!
subTitle: When an all-girl rock and roll band is captured by an evil genius, the members must do whatever it takes to stay alive.

title: Nemesis
subTitle: A car accident allows a recovery agent's prisoner, who is a serial killer, to escape into the wilderness, prompting a pursuit.

title: Primrose Lane
subTitle: Chris and Robin visit their friend's home and are surprised to find it is empty. They soon realize they are in some sort of alternate reality and not as alone as they think.
